                </div>
                <div class="jonra" data-uuid="7fed4fdca0c54ac291159135db4ec333">
                    <h2 data-uuid="526058b26785462e9c2a5c6809947f87">Fear of Communism</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="f2f3a7ce606c4742af6b6c37b88da063">In the 1950s the fear of communism caused some
                        government leaders to ignore the civil liberties of suspected Communists. Some
                        critics, like this cartoonist, believed these tactics threatened the freedom of
                        all Americans. Here, a frightened man climbs the arm of the Statue of Liberty
                        to put out her torch.</p>
                </div>
